work, and that work should contain the file", "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/pull/1082#discussion_r477388680", "createdAt": "2020-08-26T15:26:00Z", "author": {"login": "bbpennel"}, "path": "deposit/src/test/java/edu/unc/lib/deposit/normalize/DirectoryToBagJobTest.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -120,10 +120,14 @@ public void testConversion() throws Exception {\n \n         Bag childrenBag = model.getBag(folder.getURI());\n \n-        assertEquals(1, childrenBag.size());", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "cc25ad6882f7988a43479384e21316dcf1062ad6"}, "originalPosition": 4}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ3NzQyMTM1OA==", "bodyText": "This is just occurring to me now, but it'd make sense to refactor getFileResource to generate a work which wraps the file. That way it continues to be useful, the Bagit job also gets to benefit from this change, and you wouldn't have to make much (or any) changes to the behavior here.\nSo you would basically want to move all this work construction and wrapping into getFileResource, which should already correctly be handling adding to the right parent folder.", "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/pull/1082#discussion_r477421358", "createdAt": "2020-08-26T16:12:52Z", "author": {"login": "bbpennel"}, "path": "deposit/src/main/java/edu/unc/lib/deposit/normalize/DirectoryToBagJob.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -80,21 +81,32 @@ public void runJob() {\n \n             log.debug(\"Adding object {}: {}\", i++, file.getName());\n \n-            Boolean isDir = file.isDirectory();\n-\n             Path filePath = sourcePath.getParent().relativize(file.toPath());\n             String filePathString = filePath.toString();\n             String filename = filePath.getFileName().toString();\n+            Bag folderBag = getFolderBag(sourceBag, filePathString);\n+            model.add(folderBag, CdrDeposit.label, filename);\n+\n+            if (!file.isDirectory()) {\n+                // Create work object\n+                PID workPid = pidMinter.mintContentPid();\n+                Bag workBag = model.createBag(workPid.getURI());\n+                model.add(folderBag, RDF.type, Cdr.Work);\n+                model.add(folderBag, CdrDeposit.label, filename);\n \n-            if (!isDir) {\n-                Resource fileResource = getFileResource(sourceBag, filePathString);", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "cc25ad6882f7988a43479384e21316dcf1062ad6"}, "originalPosition": 46}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "5317ffba43d4ebb54b844e17fa2587e3714d89d1", "author": {"user": {"login": "lfarrell", "name": "Dean Farrell"}}, "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/commit/5317ffba43d4ebb54b844e17fa2587e3714d89d1", "committedDate": "2020-08-26T20:14:40Z", "message": "Move file wrapping to getFileResource"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "de995d8c47f28356fa02194b9abc2cd4a3fcfa58", "author": {"user": {"login": "lfarrell", "name": "Dean Farrell"}}, "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/commit/de995d8c47f28356fa02194b9abc2cd4a3fcfa58", "committedDate": "2020-08-26T20:15:45Z", "message": "Merge branch 'dir-work' of https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/Carolina-Digital-Repository into dir-work"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "aa8b2e4421ebdee3716b3fb303835e5191e4ff8e", "author": {"user": {"login": "lfarrell", "name": "Dean Farrell"}}, "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/commit/aa8b2e4421ebdee3716b3fb303835e5191e4ff8e", "committedDate": "2020-08-27T12:50:06Z", "message": "* Fix tests\n* Revert DirectoryToBagJob"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDc2OTEzMTYw", "url": "https://github.com/UNC-Libraries/box-c/pull/1082#pullrequestreview-476913160", "createdAt": "2020-08-27T16:58:49Z", "commit": {"oid": "aa8b2e4421ebdee3716b3fb303835e5191e4ff8e"}, "state": "APPROVED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"start